1.02	Century_Center_(South_Bend)	Century Center (South Bend)	The Century Center Convention Center, managed by Global Spectrum, opened in 1977 and has been managed by Global Spectrum since January, 2007. This convention center overlooks the St. Joseph River in downtown South Bend, Indiana. It features over 75,000 sq ft (7,000 m2). of convention space and is home to Island Park, an 11-acre (45,000 m2) riverfront park attached to the convention center.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/9/9e/CenturyCenterSouthBend%2CIndiana.jpg/300px-CenturyCenterSouthBend%2CIndiana.jpg
